<Content>Perfect Hotel For Everything I found this hotel on TripAdvisor and booked directly with the hotel. There was 13 of us staying in Berlin for 2 nights and this place was just right. The rooms were big, clean and fully equipt and the staff were very helpful in everyway. As for the breakfast - well the reputation is true....first class options and quality. The location was brilliant too - far enough from the centre of Berlin to not be busy and expensive, but close enough to walk in Mitte if you like. There are U  S-Bahn stations very close and also there is a 24hr bar only a few steps away. Also the area has many other bars and restaurants. Really, whatever you are lookng for in a hotel - this works for everyone! Just book it! 
